@startuml UC02_Sequence
title UC02: 修改密码 - 顺序图

actor "用户" as UserActor
boundary "修改密码界面" as PwdForm
control "密码管理控制器" as PwdController
entity "用户" as UserEntity

UserActor -> PwdForm : 输入原密码及新密码
PwdForm -> PwdController : 修改请求(oldPwd, newPwd)
PwdController -> UserEntity : validatePassword(oldPwd)
UserEntity --> PwdController : boolean

alt 原密码正确
    PwdController -> UserEntity : updatePassword(newPwd)
    UserEntity --> PwdController : success
    PwdController --> PwdForm : 成功提示
    PwdForm -> UserActor : 显示成功
else 原密码错误
    PwdController --> PwdForm : 提示错误
    PwdForm -> UserActor : 重新输入
end
@enduml
